io.fluo.recipes.transaction

Class RecordingTransactionBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.fluo.recipes.transaction.RecordingTransactionBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.fluo.api.client.SnapshotBase, io.fluo.api.client.TransactionBase
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RecordingTransaction

    public class RecordingTransactionBase
extends Object
implements io.fluo.api.client.TransactionBase
    An implementation of TransactionBase that logs all transactions operations (GET, SET, or DELETE) in a TxLog that can be used for exports
